a casino in this town?

778
00:47:13,179 --> 00:47:15,313
No.
Thank you.

779
00:47:15,381 --> 00:47:17,065
- Are you sure?
- Yeah, I'm sure.

780
00:47:17,132 --> 00:47:19,050
