01:16:56,159 --> 01:16:58,678
- Very--
- American.

1210
01:16:58,746 --> 01:17:00,813
[ Chuckles ]
American.

1211
01:17:00,881 --> 01:17:04,900
It was, actually.
It was quintessential
Americana.

1212
01:17:04,968 --> 01:17:07,987
[ Laughing ]
God bless America.

1213
01:17:08,055 --> 01:17:10,089
Oh.
[ Chuckles ]
Yeah.

1214
01:17:10,157 --> 01:17:13,660
