of Indians who might
build a casino here?

1225
01:17:45,208 --> 01:17:47,059
<i>[ Cleveland ]
It's not that they might
build this casino...</i>

1226
01:17:47,127 --> 01:17:48,711
<i>if we pay them this cash.</i>

1227
01:17:48,779 --> 01:17:50,280
<i>It's that they have to.</i>

1228
01:17:50,347 --> 01:17:53,516
