1260
01:19:33,467 --> 01:19:35,752
<i>5:00, at the courthouse.</i>

1261
01:19:35,819 --> 01:19:38,054
Our leaders are lying.
Casino corruption.

1262
01:19:38,122 --> 01:19:41,624
<i>[ Phone Ringing ]</i>

1263
01:19:41,691 --> 01:19:44,326
Hello.

1264
01:19:44,394 --> 01:19:46,295
